        <li><a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/computing/computer-science/algorithms" target="_blank">Khan Academy - Algorithms</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Coding Challenges:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.hackerrank.com/" target="_blank">HackerRank</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://codeforces.com/" target="_blank">Codeforces</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.codechef.com/" target="_blank">CodeChef</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Interview Questions:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://leetcode.com/explore/interview/card/top-interview-questions-easy/" target="_blank">LeetCode - Top Interview Questions (Easy)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://leetcode.com/explore/interview/card/top-interview-questions-medium/" target="_blank">LeetCode - Top Interview Questions (Medium)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://leetcode.com/explore/interview/card/top-interview-questions-hard/" target="_blank">LeetCode - Top Interview Questions (Hard)</a></li>
    </ul>

